          'csslint-bin' option now defaults to ``bin/csslint``; documentation was
          updated (closes #20).
          [hvelarde]
        
        - Implement removal of pre-commit hook.
          Fixes https://github.com/plone/plone.recipe.codeanalysis/issues/21
          [hvelarde]
        
        
